### Backend API quick tests
### Paste a fresh Firebase ID token below when you want to test protected routes.
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3001/api
@authToken = PASTE_FIREBASE_ID_TOKEN_HERE
@childId = REPLACE_CHILD_ID

### Health check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### Supabase connection health
GET {{baseUrl}}/database/health

### Current authenticated Firebase user
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### List children for current user
GET {{baseUrl}}/children
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Create a child
POST {{baseUrl}}/children
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Emma Vu",
  "birthDate": "2025-11-18",
  "notes": "Loves contact naps and bottle feeding.",
  "photo": ""
}

### Get one child by id
GET {{baseUrl}}/children/{{childId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Update a child
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/children/{{childId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Emma Nguyen Vu",
  "notes": "Now tracking a more regular bedtime routine."
}

### Delete a child
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/children/{{childId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### List feedings for a child
GET {{baseUrl}}/children/{{childId}}/feedings
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Create a feeding log
POST {{baseUrl}}/children/{{childId}}/feedings
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "timestamp": "2026-03-29T14:30:00.000Z",
  "type": "bottle",
  "amount": 120,
  "unit": "ml",
  "notes": "Finished the full bottle calmly."
}

### List sleep logs for a child
GET {{baseUrl}}/children/{{childId}}/sleeps
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Create a sleep log
POST {{baseUrl}}/children/{{childId}}/sleeps
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "startTime": "2026-03-29T20:15:00.000Z",
  "endTime": "2026-03-29T21:05:00.000Z",
  "notes": "Short evening nap"
}

### List diaper logs for a child
GET {{baseUrl}}/children/{{childId}}/diapers
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Create a diaper log
POST {{baseUrl}}/children/{{childId}}/diapers
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "timestamp": "2026-03-29T16:40:00.000Z",
  "type": "wet",
  "notes": "Quick change after feeding"
}

### List health logs for a child
GET {{baseUrl}}/children/{{childId}}/health-logs
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Create a health log
POST {{baseUrl}}/children/{{childId}}/health-logs
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "timestamp": "2026-03-29T18:15:00.000Z",
  "type": "symptom",
  "title": "Mild fever",
  "notes": "Temperature was 37.8C after nap."
}

### List invites for a child
GET {{baseUrl}}/children/{{childId}}/invites
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Create an invite
POST {{baseUrl}}/children/{{childId}}/invites
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "inviteeEmail": "caregiver@example.com",
  "childName": "Emma"
}

### Decline an invite
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/children/{{childId}}/invites/REPLACE_INVITE_ID/decline
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### List incoming invites for current account
GET {{baseUrl}}/invites/me
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Accept an incoming invite
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/invites/REPLACE_INVITE_ID/accept
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Decline an incoming invite
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/invites/REPLACE_INVITE_ID/decline
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### AI chat reply for a child
POST {{baseUrl}}/children/{{childId}}/ai-chat
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "Give me a summary of today"
}
